metadata.description: The Super Skills League is a Decentralized Organization (DO) with a mission to one day be a Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO) that provides grants to developers for open source projects related to web3 and education. The SuperSkills League aims to provide a public good backbone for developers who are passionate about public goods, open source software, and the future of education and employment.
metadata.name: Debbie Purifoy
